headline: The Home Depot to Host Fourth Quarter & Fiscal Year Earnings Conference Call on February 24
summary: The Home Depot®, the world's largest home improvement retailer, announced today that it will hold its Fourth Quarter & Fiscal Year Earnings Conference Call on Tuesday, February 24, at 9 a.m. ET.
